卻是當權者步步進逼，除了走上街頭，手無寸鐵的市民還能用什麼方式表達不滿？<br />\n<br />\n當你天真的以為他們會悔過時，別忘了還有8.11&mdash;更黑暗的一天<br />\n<br />\n當管治者不斷破壞我們的核心價值，新聞自由、集會自由、言論自由不斷被扼殺，我們的法制、人權受到破壞，誠信、廉潔蕩然無存的情況下，當面對欺壓，我們選擇視若無睹，當我們選擇繼續沉默，香港的核心價值將在無聲中死去。你願意站岀來為自己、為下一代爭取更好的香港嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你班連登傻仔，入乜撚嘢機場？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1460800\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1460800</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4d848b7efedcd0454609197f816bcf383c73e223","tid":1461292,"uid":187950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"收工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eab77bc3a0ca96bef67d22557aebe7e09f784924","tid":1461292,"uid":42912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:28:21.000Z","msg":"一陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7668b36eb6518998c919c9fee243c4d91684242a","tid":1461292,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"721 811"},{"pid":"88055a536a19f5b0964f901c643d53d3a81792cf","tid":1461292,"uid":264246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:28:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9bb8db0baedec511455ec97fcc1e680697532444","tid":1461292,"uid":62027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T07:33:29.000Z","msg":"收工去機場呀！<im